data.name: RoleGroupOverrides_GroupList
data.query:
SELECT
	cf_GroupName,
    GroupID,
    cf_System,
    COUNT(MemberID) as MemberCount
FROM f_App_RoleGroupOverrides_GroupList
GROUP BY cf_GroupName,GroupID,cf_System
ORDER BY cf_GroupName
